{"tid":1452990,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[警告] 如果和理非再唔升級， 你同殺人兇手冇分別！","createTime":"2019-08-12T02:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:39:02.000Z","uid":28951,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9bb67d0a98c2c08c2f3cfc1b8eeef1b7d544ac40","tid":1452990,"uid":28951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"100萬人遊行，政府冇回應。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警方暴力升級。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n200萬人遊行，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政府繼續冇回應。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警方暴力繼續升級，濫捕，直接射殺市民。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n整個六月，你有去遊行，但你得到啲乜嘢？<br />\n有，就係手足<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不斷犧牲</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n七月，警黑合作全面暴光，人人自危。<br />\n恐襲式攻擊市民，手足入院，永久性傷殘。<br />\n<br />\n你想遊行示威？ 仲以為呢個方法有用？<br />\n對唔住，你連唯一嘅機會都冇。<br />\n仲唔明？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">依家政府直接同你講:收聲啦，你哋好噪啊。</span><br />\n<br />\n一直講緊和理非要升級，唔係叫你前線食彈。只係叫你三罷都話唔支持，不合作運動又屌人阻住你返工。<br />\n<br />\n就係你哋一直冇行動先令前線不斷升級，不斷去面對危險。<br />\n每日淨係睇直播話睇到喊，心痛。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有用咩？</span><br />\n<br />\n依家政府就係睇死你哋所謂嘅和理非乜都做唔出先不斷升級暴力，到有一日前線冇曬人，佢做乜都得。<br />\n<br />\n你繼續咁落去，同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">送前線去死</span></span>冇咩分別？<br />\n請各位自稱和理非諗吓，你係咪要繼續你所謂嘅抗爭有冇用。<br />\n諗完唔該你哋要有行動，唔係得個口講支持。"},{"pid":"0dac888e9f360c2968880bbb7ade251cda92891a","tid":1452990,"uid":28951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:03:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">有人性既你，請你今日罷工去機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1452011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1452011</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"5cbdeecc1ab27e9f62a8ab20cd3985ba92cdeb97","tid":1452990,"uid":28951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:26:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190812/59922249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F59922249&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=559cac02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F59922249&h=35c1daf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190812/59922249</a><br />\n<br />\n民建聯譚耀宗：警「誤中」不足為奇<br />\n惟人大常委、民建聯譚耀宗昨卻為警暴護航，宣稱警察兩個月來疲於奔命，欠缺休息，又不能回家，真是很辛苦，有時電光火石一刻，影響判斷，即使有時「誤中」，亦不足為奇，呼籲市民體諒。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲要為呢個政權撐幾耐？</span></span>"},{"pid":"f136fa386441c4c935c42d054f035a662f31db6e","tid":1452990,"uid":32719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:26:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RntuKxi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRntuKxi.jpg&h=2d720f36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kNktfDZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkNktfDZ.jpg&h=5d6abd42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gk0wXSn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgk0wXSn.jpg&h=b2d98c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dV4xHi5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdV4xHi5.jpg&h=8aeecf39&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WrKE6LM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrKE6LM.png&h=b9706757&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DL2GAD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDL2GAD7.png&h=2d6e2c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARU9Kxu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARU9Kxu.png&h=a32d7290&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ki2Wpxw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"h